看来那些 UFO 出自那个地方, 但目击报告有几百起

22
00:01:20,787 --> 00:01:21,900
<font color="gray">Aye, they must have quite an army by now.</font>
是, 他们目前肯定有很大一支队伍了

23
00:01:21,987 --> 00:01:24,376
<font color="gray">- The thing is, where are they hiding them all?</font>
