36
00:01:57,987 --> 00:01:59,215
<font color="gray">Oh, for heaven's sake.</font>
噢, 老天爷啊

37
00:01:59,307 --> 00:02:00,979
<font color="gray">If you can't trust a UNIT force, who can you trust?</font>
如果你连 UNIT 都信不过, 你能信谁?

38
