<font color="gray">There's nothing we...</font>
没有什么我们...

39
00:02:04,907 --> 00:02:08,900
<font color="gray">- What's the matter?</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh. Nothing. Nothing at all.</font>
- 怎么了?   - 噢, 没事, 完全没事

40
00:02:08,987 --> 00:02:12,536
<font color="gray">Look, Billy, Vaughn's a powerful chap, I know that.</font>
你看, Billy, Vaughn 是个有能量的家伙, 这我知道

41
00:02:12,627 --> 00:02:15,460
<font color="gray">But surely we can at least</font>
<font color="gray">request a thorough investigation.</font>
但我们至少应该可以申请进行全面调查啊

42
00:02:15,547 --> 00:02:17,299
<font color="gray">This isn't our province.</font>
这不在我们职权范围内

43
00:02:17,387 --> 00:02:20,697
<font color="gray">- Well, then whose province is it?</font>
<font color="gray">- It's no good getting angry about this.</font>
