我肯定这都是误会. 我会亲自同总司令沟通内部安全的问题

48
00:02:33,627 --> 00:02:35,103
<font color="gray">But, Billy, talk isn't going to help.</font>
但是, Bily, 沟通并没有什么帮助

49
00:02:35,227 --> 00:02:37,063
<font color="gray">I want some sort of action, and I want it now.</font>
我想要的是某种行动, 并且现在就要

50
00:02:37,147 --> 00:02:39,422
<font color="gray">At least get the civil authorities to investigate.</font>
至少要拿到启动调查的授权

51
00:02:39,507 --> 00:02:42,544
<font color="gray">You'll have to leave this matter with me.</font>
你就只能把这个问题交给我了

52
00:02:43,307 --> 00:02:44,899
<font color="gray">Will I?</font>
是么?

53
00:02:44,987 --> 00:02:47,137
<font color="gray">If you're thinking of going to the C in C yourself,</font>
如果你想自己去找总司令

54
00:02:47,227 --> 00:02:49,422
<font color="gray">I shouldn't bother, you'll be wasting your time.</font>
我不会干涉, 你只是在浪费自己的时间

55
00:02:49,507 --> 00:02:51,782
<font color="gray">So you're going to do nothing?</font>
这么说你打算什么都不做?

56
00:02:53,267 --> 00:02:57,499
<font color="gray">- What sort of hold has Vaughn got on you?</font>
<font color="gray">- Vaughn? I...</font>
- Vaughn 拿到了你什么把柄?   - Vaughn? 我...

57
00:02:58,867 --> 00:03:03,856
<font color="gray">Brigadier, your UNIT force will take no precipitous</font>
<font color="gray">action without top-priority permission.</font>
准将, 你的 UNIT 小组没有拿到最高授权之前, 不得擅自行动

58
00:03:03,987 --> 00:03:07,536
<font color="gray">- That is an order.  - I see, sir.</font>
