如果你到指挥中心去讲这个故事, 他们会认为你疯了

84
00:04:29,627 --> 00:04:31,185
<font color="gray">Yes. Yes, Jimmy, you're right.</font>
是的, 是的, Jimmy, 你说得对

85
00:04:31,267 --> 00:04:34,862
<font color="gray">'Course, what we really need is</font>
