00:05:15,267 --> 00:05:16,584
<font color="gray">Mr Vaughn, I don't think you should...</font>
Vaughn 先生, 我觉得你不应该...

97
00:05:16,667 --> 00:05:19,536
<font color="gray">- We must try the machine, Gregory.</font>
