- 我们必须试试这台机器, Gregory  - 但这很危险

98
00:05:19,627 --> 00:05:22,585
<font color="gray">It would be even more dangerous</font>
<font color="gray">if we didn't try it.</font>
如果我们不试一下的话, 就会更加危险

99
00:05:22,707 --> 00:05:25,744
<font color="gray">We must be sure we have an effective weapon</font>
<font color="gray">against the Cybermen.</font>
我们必须得确保我们有一个有效的武器来对付赛博人

100
00:05:25,827 --> 00:05:28,660
<font color="gray">- You're going to try it on one of them?</font>
<font color="gray">- Why not?</font>
- 你打算在他们身上做试验?   - 为什么不呢?

101
00:05:39,067 --> 00:05:44,221
<font color="gray">Revive it. Uh, just enough</font>
<font color="gray">to bring it out of its cocoon.</font>
弄醒它.  啊, 把它从茧里面弄出来就可以了

102
00:05:44,307 --> 00:05:45,786
<font color="gray">MAN: Yes, sir.</font>
好的, 先生

