<font color="gray">VAUGHN: More power!</font>
<font color="gray">GREGORY: That's all there is!</font>
- 再开大!  - 已经是最大了!

113
00:07:23,427 --> 00:07:25,019
<font color="gray">(GUN FIRING)</font>

