00:07:28,027 --> 00:07:29,016
<font color="gray">VAUGHN: Quick!</font>
快!

115
00:07:32,627 --> 00:07:34,738
<font color="gray">I told you, the machine isn't ready yet.</font>
我告诉过你, 这台机器还没有准备好

116
00:07:35,187 --> 00:07:38,224
<font color="gray">- It's following the others into the sewers.</font>
<font color="gray">- Let it go.</font>
- 它跟着它的同伴进入了下水道  - 让它去吧

117
00:07:38,307 --> 00:07:40,423
<font color="gray">It's gone mad. It could've killed us all.</font>
