00:15:10,584 --> 00:15:13,157
<font color="gray">Vaughn's going to use it as a weapon against the Cybermen,</font>
Vaughn 打算把它用作对付赛博人的武器

241
00:15:13,284 --> 00:15:14,657
<font color="gray">once he has no further use for them.</font>
-- 一旦他用不着它们了之后

242
00:15:14,744 --> 00:15:16,257
<font color="gray">- What, the Professor's machine?  - Yes.</font>
- 什么, 教授的机器吗?   - 是的

243
00:15:16,344 --> 00:15:20,257
<font color="gray">Emotion is alien to the Cybermen's</font>
<font color="gray">nervous system. It'll destroy it.</font>
情感对于赛博人的神经系统是异物, 会杀死它

244
00:15:21,864 --> 00:15:24,332
<font color="gray">The micromonolithic circuits.</font>
那些微型单晶片电路

245
00:15:24,424 --> 00:15:27,994
<font color="gray">They're emotional circuits!</font>
<font color="gray">No wonder they weren't logical.</font>
它们是情感电路!  怪不得它们在逻辑上说不通了

246
00:15:28,084 --> 00:15:32,057
<font color="gray">Now, why didn't I think of this before?</font>
<font color="gray">Now, let's see.</font>
啊, 为什么我早没有想到? 来, 我们看看

247
00:15:32,144 --> 00:15:35,056
<font color="gray">- Now what's he up to? - I've no idea.</font>
- 现在他在搞什么?   - 我不知道

248
00:16:00,684 --> 00:16:05,280
<font color="gray">The micromonolithic circuits are</font>
<font color="gray">artificial nervous systems.</font>
这些微型单晶体电路是人工的神经系统

249
00:16:05,364 --> 00:16:09,277
<font color="gray">Once activated they will produce</font>
<font color="gray">the Cyber-hypnotic force</font>
一旦激活, 他们可以产生网络催眠的力量

250
00:16:09,364 --> 00:16:11,400
<font color="gray">that controls human beings.</font>
能够控制人类

251
00:16:11,484 --> 00:16:14,518
<font color="gray">But there are hundreds, thousands</font>
<font color="gray">of these circuits in IE equipment</font>
但有成百上千的 IE 公司设备都有这种电路

252
00:16:14,619 --> 00:16:15,980
<font color="gray">- all over the world.</font>
<font color="gray">- Exactly!</font>
- 遍布全世界  - 正是!

253
00:16:16,084 --> 00:16:18,077
<font color="gray">So everyone will come under their control.</font>
所以所有人都会被他们控制

254
00:16:18,164 --> 00:16:20,473
<font color="gray">Yes, the Cybermen will take over everybody.</font>
是的, 赛博人会控制每个人

255
00:16:20,564 --> 00:16:21,838
<font color="gray">Well, isn't there anything that we can do?</font>
那, 有什么我们可以做的吗?

256
00:16:21,924 --> 00:16:25,041
<font color="gray">Yes, there is a way to block the signals,</font>
<font color="gray">isn't there, Zoe?</font>
有, 有一种方法可以屏蔽这种讯号, 对不, Zoe?

257
00:16:25,124 --> 00:16:26,318
<font color="gray">The depolariser.</font>
消偏振器

258
00:16:26,404 --> 00:16:29,521
<font color="gray">Worn at the back of the neck,</font>
<font color="gray">it will jam the Cyber-control waves.</font>
只要套在脖子后面, 它就可以阻塞赛博控制波

259
00:16:29,604 --> 00:16:31,879
<font color="gray">Yes. Have you any neuristors here, Professor?</font>
是的. 你这里有神经元器件吗, 博士?

260
00:16:31,964 --> 00:16:35,400
<font color="gray">- Well, a few, I think.</font>
<font color="gray">- Zoe, show the Professor what to do.</font>
- 哦, 有一些, 我想  - Zoe, 告诉博士该怎么做

261
00:16:35,484 --> 00:16:37,395
<font color="gray">The invasion could come at any moment.</font>
入侵可能随时发生

262
00:16:38,004 --> 00:16:39,881
<font color="gray">(ALARM SOUNDING)</font>

263
00:16:45,524 --> 00:16:46,513
<font color="gray">(WHIRRING)</font>

264
00:16:51,364 --> 00:16:54,993
<font color="gray"><i>- Is all in readiness?</i></font>
<font color="gray">- Of course.</font>
- 都准备好了吗?   - 当然

265
00:16:55,084 --> 00:16:59,236
<font color="gray"><i>There is one hour to invasion time.</i></font>
离入侵时间还有一小时

266
00:16:59,364 --> 00:17:03,676
<font color="gray"><i>- Countdown will start from now.</i></font>
<font color="gray">- Excellent.</font>
- 现在开始倒计时  - 太好了

267
00:17:04,804 --> 00:17:08,114
<font color="gray"><i>We are moving into position now.</i></font>
我们现在各就各位

268
00:17:08,204 --> 00:17:11,913
<font color="gray"><i>Ready to transmit the Cyber-signal.</i></font>
准备开始传送赛博讯号

269
00:17:21,084 --> 00:17:22,836
<font color="gray">(SIGNAL HUMMING)</font>

270
00:17:50,412 --> 00:17:52,323
<font color="gray">(DOOR BUZZING)</font>

271
00:17:55,532 --> 00:17:56,726
<font color="gray">Packer.</font>
Packer

272
00:17:57,132 --> 00:17:58,360
<font color="gray"><i>Yes, sir.</i></font>
在,先生

273
00:17:58,452 --> 00:18:01,330
<font color="gray">- Have you discovered where the Professor is?</font>
<font color="gray"><i>- Yes, Mr Vaughn.</i></font>
- 你发现教授在哪里了吗?   - 是的, Vaughn 先生

274
00:18:01,412 --> 00:18:02,891
<font color="gray">Go and collect him.</font>
去把他弄回来

275
00:18:03,092 --> 00:18:06,721
<font color="gray">I want work started on the production</font>
<font color="gray">of the machines immediately.</font>
我期望机器的生产工作可以立即开始

276
00:18:07,132 --> 00:18:09,123
<font color="gray">Go and recapture Watkins.</font>
去把 Watkins 重新抓回来

277
00:18:09,412 --> 00:18:12,590
<font color="gray">Don't let anything or anyone stop you.</font>
不要让任何事、任何人阻止你

278
00:18:18,812 --> 00:18:20,591
<font color="gray">- Oh, thanks!  - Thank goodness you made it.</font>
- 哦, 谢谢!   - 感谢老天你闯过来了

279
00:18:20,672 --> 00:18:22,742
<font color="gray">- Any trouble?  - Hundreds of Cybermen about, sir.</font>
- 有问题吗?   - 周围有百多个赛博人, 长官

280
00:18:22,832 --> 00:18:25,107
<font color="gray">The sooner we get out of here, the better.</font>
<font color="gray">Everybody ready?</font>
我们越早离开这里越好, 都准备好了吗?

281
00:18:25,192 --> 00:18:27,069
<font color="gray">- ALL: Yes!</font>
<font color="gray">- ISOBEL: Yes, we're ready, we're coming.</font>
- 准备好了!  - 是的, 我们准备好了, 我们来了

282
00:18:27,152 --> 00:18:28,346
<font color="gray">Listen!</font>
听!

283
00:18:30,832 --> 00:18:32,550
<font color="gray">(TYRES SCREECHING)</font>

284
00:18:35,312 --> 00:18:38,668
<font color="gray">We'd better get out of here,</font>
<font color="gray">out of the back way as quickly as possible.</font>
我们最好离开这里, 尽快离开这后面

285
00:18:38,752 --> 00:18:41,346
<font color="gray">- Right!  - Come on, move, everybody. Quickly!</font>
- 好!   - 快点, 动起来, 所有人, 快!

286
00:18:41,432 --> 00:18:43,229
<font color="gray">Out of the back door. Hurry it up.</font>
从后门出去, 快点动起来

287
00:18:43,312 --> 00:18:45,348
<font color="gray">Come on, Jamie. Professor, all right? Good.</font>
快点, Jamie. 教授, 没事吧?  好

288
00:18:45,432 --> 00:18:46,501
<font color="gray">(GUN FIRING)</font>

289
00:18:51,972 --> 00:18:55,044
<font color="gray">- Yes, Jimmy, where are you?</font>
<font color="gray">- TURNER: <i>In bother, sir. We need help.</i></font>
- 是的, Jimmy, 你在哪里?  - 遇到麻烦了, 长官, 我们需要帮助

290
00:18:55,132 --> 00:18:57,441
<font color="gray"><i>- Can you give us a chopper?</i></font>
<font color="gray">- Yes.</font>
- 你能给我们派一架直升机吗?   - 可以

291
00:18:58,532 --> 00:19:02,241
<font color="gray">- Can you make sector five?</font>
<font color="gray"><i>- We can try, sir.</i></font>
- 你们能赶到第五区吗?   - 我们可以试试, 长官

292
00:19:02,332 --> 00:19:04,448
<font color="gray">Right, I'll get the chopper there. Out.</font>
好, 我让直升机去那里, 挂了

293
00:19:06,752 --> 00:19:09,312
<font color="gray">How could they escape the Cyber-control?</font>
他们怎么能摆脱赛博控制?

294
00:19:09,392 --> 00:19:11,383
<font color="gray">It's that Doctor, something to do with him.</font>
是那个博士, 跟他有点关系

295
00:19:11,472 --> 00:19:13,110
<font color="gray">You should've got rid of him</font>
<font color="gray">when you had the chance.</font>
你有机会的时候应该干掉他的

296
00:19:13,192 --> 00:19:14,784
<font color="gray">Shut up, Packer!</font>
闭嘴, Packer!

297
00:19:18,272 --> 00:19:19,864
<font color="gray">I must go on with the invasion.</font>
我必须去继续推进入侵的事情

298
00:19:19,952 --> 00:19:22,386
<font color="gray">But what about the Professor?</font>
但教授怎么处理?

299
00:19:22,472 --> 00:19:24,401
<font color="gray">Without him, we can't make any more machines.</font>
没有他, 我们制造不了任何机器

300
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:26,511
<font color="gray">Without machines, we can't control the Cybermen.</font>
没有机器, 我们控制不了赛博人

301
00:19:26,592 --> 00:19:28,548
<font color="gray">Let me worry about that.</font>
让我来操心这个事吧

302
00:19:29,392 --> 00:19:33,988
<font color="gray">For the moment, I have the Cybermen</font>
<font color="gray">exactly where I want them.</font>
就目前而言, 赛博人正好在我期望它们所在的位置

303
00:19:34,072 --> 00:19:35,790
<font color="gray">Yeah, but for how long?</font>
是, 但会持续多久?

304
00:19:35,872 --> 00:19:38,989
<font color="gray">Now, can you honestly say</font>
<font color="gray">that everything's going according to plan?</font>
现在, 你能否实话告诉我, 是不是所有事情都会按计划走?

305
00:19:39,072 --> 00:19:41,142
<font color="gray">That nothing's been overlooked?</font>
<font color="gray">Well, can you?</font>
没有漏掉什么吧? 怎样, 能吗?

306
00:19:41,232 --> 00:19:43,029
<font color="gray">Just obey my orders!</font>
服从我的命令就是!

307
00:19:44,112 --> 00:19:47,422
<font color="gray">Now, get in touch with the compound</font>
<font color="gray">and have the radio beam projected.</font>
现在, 联系工业园, 将无线电信号发送出去

308
00:19:47,512 --> 00:19:49,503
<font color="gray">The invasion fleet must be brought in.</font>
必须得把入侵的舰队带进来

309
00:19:50,112 --> 00:19:52,307
<font color="gray">Now, Doctor, we must deal with</font>
<font color="gray">this invasion you say is coming.</font>
现在, 博士, 你所说的即将来临的这场入侵, 我们必须对付它

310
00:19:52,392 --> 00:19:54,668
<font color="gray">Yes, at least we know where they'll land.</font>
是的, 至少我们知道他们会在那里着陆

311
00:19:54,792 --> 00:19:57,068
<font color="gray">They'll home in on Vaughn's radio signal.</font>
它们会沿着 Vaughn 的无线电讯号过来

312
00:19:57,152 --> 00:20:00,110
<font color="gray">Would we be able to pick them off</font>
<font color="gray">with anti-missile missiles?</font>
我们能够用反导导弹拦截它们吗?

313
00:20:00,192 --> 00:20:02,023
<font color="gray">Yes, that's a good idea.</font>
<font color="gray">We might have a try.</font>
嗯, 这是一个好主意. 我们可以试一试

314
00:20:02,112 --> 00:20:04,831
<font color="gray">Right. There's a base near Henlow Downs.</font>
<font color="gray">Er, just a minute.</font>
好, 在 Henlow Downs 附近有一个基地. 呃, 等一下

315
00:20:04,912 --> 00:20:09,144
<font color="gray">- Sergeant Walters?</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, Zoe, sit down, dear. It's a bit bumpy.</font>
- Walters 中士吗?   - 噢, Zoe, 坐下, 有一点颠簸

316
00:20:09,232 --> 00:20:11,905
<font color="gray">- Now, how's Jamie's leg?</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, it's just a slight flesh wound.</font>
- 现在 Jamie 的脚怎样了?   - 哦, 只是有点轻微的皮外伤

317
00:20:11,992 --> 00:20:14,267
<font color="gray">But he's furious, because the Army doctor</font>
<font color="gray">won't let him walk on it.</font>
但他吵得厉害, 因为军队医生不让他走路

318
00:20:14,352 --> 00:20:16,070
<font color="gray">Well, he would be, wouldn't he?</font>
<font color="gray">How's the Professor?</font>
啊, 他会的, 对吧? 教授怎样?

319
00:20:16,152 --> 00:20:17,380
<font color="gray">Oh, he'll be all right.</font>
<font color="gray">Isobel's with him.</font>
噢, 他会没事的. Isobel 在陪着他

320
00:20:17,472 --> 00:20:18,461
<font color="gray">(DOCTOR SIGHS)</font>

321
00:20:18,552 --> 00:20:20,861
<font color="gray">- Anything I can do, Doctor?</font>
<font color="gray">- Well, I...</font>
- 我能做点什么吗, 博士?   - 唔, 我...

322
00:20:20,952 --> 00:20:23,625
<font color="gray">I suggest that you...</font>
<font color="gray">you go with the Brigadier.</font>
我建议你...你跟准将走

323
00:20:23,712 --> 00:20:26,272
<font color="gray">As much as I detest computers, I...</font>
鉴于我如此讨厌电脑, 我...

324
00:20:26,352 --> 00:20:28,912
<font color="gray">I think that remarkable brain of yours</font>
<font color="gray">will come in very handy.</font>
我觉得你那聪明的脑袋瓜会更有用

325
00:20:28,992 --> 00:20:30,710
<font color="gray">Right. What are you going to do?</font>
好. 你打算做什么?

326
00:20:30,792 --> 00:20:34,944
<font color="gray">I think it's about time I had</font>
<font color="gray">a serious talk with our Mr Vaughn.</font>
我觉得是时候去跟我们的 Vaughn 先生进行一次严肃的谈话了

327
00:20:35,032 --> 00:20:37,910
<font color="gray">What, go back?</font>
<font color="gray">But he'd kill you as soon as look at you.</font>
什么, 又回去? 但他会一看见你就杀了你的

328
00:20:37,992 --> 00:20:41,462
<font color="gray">No, we need time</font>
<font color="gray">if we're going to stop this attack,</font>
不, 我们需要时间, 如果我们想要阻止这场攻击的话

329
00:20:41,552 --> 00:20:43,782
<font color="gray">and I think I can get us that time.</font>
而我觉得我可以帮我们争取到那些时间

330
00:20:43,872 --> 00:20:46,432
<font color="gray">No, this is madness.</font>
<font color="gray">I can't afford to let you take that risk.</font>
不, 这太疯狂了. 让你去冒险, 我承担不起这责

331
00:20:46,512 --> 00:20:48,582
<font color="gray">You can't afford not to, Brigadier.</font>
不让我去的话, 你也承担不起, 准将

332
00:20:48,672 --> 00:20:50,822
<font color="gray">If you're going to attack</font>
<font color="gray">the Cybermen with missiles,</font>
如果你打算用导弹攻击这些赛博人

333
00:20:50,912 --> 00:20:53,267
<font color="gray">they're going to retaliate,</font>
<font color="gray">and we want to know how and with what.</font>
他们就会反击, 我们需要知道用什么方式、什么武器

334
00:20:53,352 --> 00:20:56,988
<font color="gray">- But how can you find that out?</font>
<font color="gray">- I'll leave my radio on</font>
- 但你怎么能搞到那些信息?   - 我会把无线电开着

335
00:20:57,072 --> 00:21:00,182
<font color="gray">and then you'll hear every word</font>
<font color="gray">that passes between me and Vaughn.</font>
你们就能听到我和 Vaughn 之间的每一个字

336
00:21:00,272 --> 00:21:03,503
<font color="gray">But you'll never get near the place.</font>
<font color="gray">The whole area will be crawling with Cybermen.</font>
但你不能靠近那个地方, 那里将会挤满了赛博人

337
00:21:03,592 --> 00:21:05,742
<font color="gray">Oh, there's one place</font>
<font color="gray">where there'll be no Cybermen.</font>
哦, 有一个地方不会有赛博人

338
00:21:05,832 --> 00:21:07,709
<font color="gray">- Where's that?  - In the sewers.</font>
- 哪里?   - 下水道里

339
00:21:17,392 --> 00:21:20,384
<font color="gray">UNIT Control. This is the Doctor.</font>
UNIT 控制中心, 我是博士

340
00:21:21,112 --> 00:21:25,344
<font color="gray">- Is Brigadier there, please?</font>
<font color="gray">- WALTERS: <i>Hold on a moment, sir, I'll get him.</i></font>
- 准将在吗, 请问?   - 等一下, 先生, 我去叫他

341
00:21:25,432 --> 00:21:26,660
<font color="gray">(STATIC BUZZING)</font>

342
00:21:31,232 --> 00:21:32,551
<font color="gray">BRIGADIER: <i>Yes, Doctor, go ahead.</i></font>
好了, 博士, 请说

343
00:21:32,632 --> 00:21:36,068
<font color="gray">Er, Brigadier, I've just entered the sewers.</font>
呃, 准将, 我刚刚进入了下水道

344
00:21:36,152 --> 00:21:38,950
<font color="gray">I'm going to make my way to Vaughn's headquarters.</font>
正要前往 Vaughn 的总部

345
00:21:39,032 --> 00:21:41,341
<font color="gray">I'll give you a call when I get there.</font>
等我到了那里我会呼你

346
00:21:41,432 --> 00:21:43,263
<font color="gray"><i>Right. We'll have a chopper in the area</i></font>
好, 我们会安排一架直升机守那个区域

347
00:21:43,352 --> 00:21:46,071
<font color="gray">- <i>in case you get in trouble.</i></font>
<font color="gray">- Thank you.</font>
- 以防你万一遇到麻烦  - 谢谢你

348
00:21:48,792 --> 00:21:50,908
<font color="gray">(WATER DRIPPING)</font>

349
00:22:00,052 --> 00:22:04,170
<font color="gray">And all the main communication centres</font>
<font color="gray">are now manned by our forces?</font>
所有的主通讯中心都已经被我们的人控制了吧?

350
00:22:04,252 --> 00:22:05,765
<font color="gray">Yes, but, um...</font>
是的, 但是, 呃...

351
00:22:06,932 --> 00:22:08,843
<font color="gray">What? But what, Packer?</font>
怎么了, 但是什么, Packer?

352
00:22:08,932 --> 00:22:12,686
<font color="gray">Well, we can't make a complete takeover</font>
<font color="gray">without a full invasion force.</font>
只是, 没有一支完整的入侵队伍的话, 我们没法完全掌控

353
00:22:12,772 --> 00:22:15,889
<font color="gray">They'll arrive, Packer, they'll arrive.</font>
他们会到的, Packer, 他们会到的

354
00:22:16,372 --> 00:22:18,124
<font color="gray">And when they do,</font>
等他们到了

355
00:22:18,812 --> 00:22:23,886
<font color="gray">there won't be one city in the entire world</font>
<font color="gray">that we don't control.</font>
整个世界没有一个城市我们掌控不了

356
00:22:24,772 --> 00:22:27,445
<font color="gray">Think of it, Packer, the entire world!</font>
想想吧, Packer, 整个世界!

357
00:22:27,572 --> 00:22:28,721
<font color="gray">(ALARM SOUNDING)</font>

358
00:22:29,292 --> 00:22:31,362
<font color="gray">It's the security alarm,</font>
<font color="gray">the UNIT forces must have...</font>
是安全警报, UNIT 的队伍肯定已经...

359
00:22:31,452 --> 00:22:32,646
<font color="gray">Packer.</font>
Packer

360
00:22:34,652 --> 00:22:36,542
<font color="gray"><i>There you are.</i></font>
你在啊

361
00:22:36,692 --> 00:22:39,889
<font color="gray"><i>I hope I haven't called</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>at an inconvenient moment, but I...</i></font>
我期望我来访的时间没有给你带来不便, 但是我...

362
00:22:39,972 --> 00:22:42,805
<font color="gray"><i>I would rather like a word with you.</i></font>
我想要跟你说两句话

363
00:22:44,412 --> 00:22:47,449
<font color="gray">Clever of you to avoid our Cyber-control beam.</font>
你很聪明, 想要躲开我们的赛博控制波

364
00:22:47,532 --> 00:22:49,921
<font color="gray"><i>Oh, it was nothing.</i></font>
噢, 那没什么

365
00:22:50,332 --> 00:22:52,926
<font color="gray"><i>I'll...I'll come up, I know the way.</i></font>
我...我现在上来, 我知道路

366
00:22:54,052 --> 00:22:56,043
<font color="gray">He must be out of his mind!</font>
他肯定是失心疯了

367
00:22:56,132 --> 00:22:57,884
<font color="gray">Far from it, Packer.</font>
远远不是, Packer

368
00:22:58,372 --> 00:23:02,923
<font color="gray">Have the guards search the building,</font>
<font color="gray">just in case he's brought any friends with him.</font>
让警卫们搜索整栋大楼, 以防他带了一些朋友过来

369
00:23:03,252 --> 00:23:04,688
<font color="gray">Tell the raiding party to stand by.</font>
告诉突袭小组做好准备

370
00:23:04,772 --> 00:23:07,605
<font color="gray">- Yes, sir.</font>
<font color="gray">- DOCTOR: (WHISPERING) <i>Ah, Brigadier. Brigadier.</i></font>
- 是, 长官  - 啊, 准将, 准将

371
00:23:07,692 --> 00:23:12,720
<font color="gray">- Yes, Doctor, go ahead.</font>
<font color="gray"><i>- I am just about to enter the lion's den.</i></font>
- 收到, 博士, 继续  - 我就要进入虎穴了

372
00:23:13,132 --> 00:23:16,408
<font color="gray"><i>I will leave the radio on as of now.</i></font>
从现在开始我会让无线电一直开着

373
00:23:16,572 --> 00:23:19,245
<font color="gray">- Right. Good luck.  <i>- Thank you.</i></font>
- 好, 祝你好运  - 谢谢

374
00:23:20,292 --> 00:23:22,487
<font color="gray">Keep that channel open</font>
<font color="gray">and get the whole thing on tape.</font>
一直开着那个频道, 把整个过程录下来

375
00:23:22,572 --> 00:23:24,210
<font color="gray">- Yes, sir.  - If he yells for help while I'm away,</font>
- 是, 长官  - 如果他呼救, 而我又不在

376
00:23:24,292 --> 00:23:27,250
<font color="gray">- send in everything we've got to get him out.</font>
<font color="gray">- Right.</font>
- 就把我们手头所有的人派进去救他出来  - 好的

377
00:23:29,392 --> 00:23:32,509
<font color="gray">VAUGHN: <i>Ah, Doctor, what an unexpected pleasure.</i></font>
啊, 博士, 真是不胜荣幸啊

378
00:23:32,832 --> 00:23:34,185
<font color="gray"><i>Do come in.</i></font>
请进来

379
00:23:35,872 --> 00:23:37,828
<font color="gray">And you trust them?</font>
你信任它们吗?

380
00:23:37,912 --> 00:23:42,702
<font color="gray">Doctor, I've worked with the Cybermen</font>
<font color="gray">for five years, preparing this invasion.</font>
博士, 我同赛博人合作了五年, 共同准备这次入侵

381
00:23:43,392 --> 00:23:47,670
<font color="gray">I know them, the way they think,</font>
<font color="gray">the single-mindedness of their purpose.</font>
我了解他们, 他们的思维方式, 他们一根筋想要达到的目的

382
00:23:47,752 --> 00:23:51,427
<font color="gray">Then you must know what ruthless</font>
<font color="gray">and inhuman killers they are.</font>
那你肯定知道他们都是冷血无情的杀手吧

383
00:23:51,512 --> 00:23:52,865
<font color="gray">Of course.</font>
当然

384
00:23:52,952 --> 00:23:56,069
<font color="gray">But then, they are my allies, not my enemies.</font>
但是呢, 他们是我的同盟, 不是我的敌人

385
00:23:57,632 --> 00:24:00,669
<font color="gray">Do you really think they'll honour</font>
<font color="gray">any bargain that you make with them?</font>
你真的觉得他们会遵循你同他们谈好的交易?

386
00:24:00,752 --> 00:24:06,224
<font color="gray">Oh, I've planned this whole operation in great detail,</font>
<font color="gray">allowing for every possible factor.</font>
噢, 我策划了这整个行动, 事无巨细, 考虑了各种因素

387
00:24:06,312 --> 00:24:08,826
<font color="gray">It was I who contacted them in deep space,</font>
当初是我联系了深空中的他们

388
00:24:08,912 --> 00:24:11,551
<font color="gray">provided the means by which they travelled to Earth.</font>
给他们提供了到达地球的手段

389
00:24:11,632 --> 00:24:15,068
<font color="gray">And masterminded the whole operation from A to Z.</font>
从 A 到 Z 策划了这次行动的整个过程

390
00:24:16,032 --> 00:24:17,351
<font color="gray">(SCOFFS)</font>

391
00:24:17,912 --> 00:24:23,748
<font color="gray">They have merely provided their advanced</font>
<font color="gray">scientific skills, their might and strength.</font>
他们只不过是提供了它们的先进科技, 和一点力气

392
00:24:24,032 --> 00:24:26,148
<font color="gray">And what do they get out of all this?</font>
那他们能从这里面得到什么呢?

393
00:24:26,232 --> 00:24:31,352
<font color="gray">What they want and what they're going to get</font>
<font color="gray">are two entirely different things.</font>
他们想要什么和他们会得到什么, 是两件完全不同的事

394
00:24:31,432 --> 00:24:33,821
<font color="gray">Oh, you're a fool, Vaughn.</font>
噢, 你是个傻瓜, Vaughn

395
00:24:33,912 --> 00:24:36,949
<font color="gray">When they get here, they'll take over.</font>
一旦他们到了这里, 他们就会夺取控制权

396
00:24:37,032 --> 00:24:40,707
<font color="gray">All Cybermen here are conditioned to obey my orders.</font>
根据条件, 所有赛博人都要服从我的命令

397
00:24:40,792 --> 00:24:43,022
<font color="gray">They are directly under my command.</font>
他们都受我直接指挥

398
00:24:43,112 --> 00:24:47,071
<font color="gray">Oh, possibly. But what about the others,</font>
<font color="gray">out there in space?</font>
噢, 有可能. 但另外那些呢, 在太空里的那些?

399
00:24:47,152 --> 00:24:50,269
<font color="gray">Are they conditioned to obey your commands?</font>
他们也会按条件服从你的指挥?

400
00:24:50,352 --> 00:24:52,912
<font color="gray">If they're not, I'll destroy them.</font>
如果他们不服从, 我会消灭他们

401
00:24:52,992 --> 00:24:55,187
<font color="gray">- With the Professor's machine?  - Yes.</font>
- 就用教授的机器?   - 是的

402
00:24:55,272 --> 00:24:57,228
<font color="gray">With one machine?</font>
就凭一台机器?

403
00:24:57,712 --> 00:24:59,748
<font color="gray">I'll have more made.</font>
我会多制造一些的

404
00:24:59,832 --> 00:25:03,347
<font color="gray">But you'll have to have the Professor's</font>
<font color="gray">help to do that, won't you?</font>
但你得需要教授的帮助才能做到, 对吧?

405
00:25:03,432 --> 00:25:05,150
<font color="gray">We've got the Professor.</font>
教授在我们手上

406
00:25:05,232 --> 00:25:07,587
<font color="gray">They'll be under my command,</font>
<font color="gray">exactly like the others.</font>
它们会听我指挥的, 跟其它的完全一样

407
00:25:07,672 --> 00:25:10,345
<font color="gray">But you can't be sure of that, can you?</font>
但对此你并没有把握, 对吧?

408
00:25:15,312 --> 00:25:18,031
<font color="gray">(ELECTRONIC SIGNAL PULSATING)</font>

409
00:25:18,152 --> 00:25:20,950
<font color="gray">Well, we can't get them all.</font>
<font color="gray">Let's take as many as we can.</font>
好吧, 我们没法把它们全干掉, 能搞定多少就算多少

410
00:25:21,032 --> 00:25:24,866
<font color="gray">- Lift off the activation check.</font>
<font color="gray">- Coordinate programme running, sir.</font>
- 开始激活检查  - 协同程序已经开始运行, 长官

411
00:25:26,432 --> 00:25:29,788
<font color="gray">- Link programme to telemeter guidance.</font>
<font color="gray">- PETERS: Roger.</font>
- 将程序连接到测距导航仪  - 收到

412
00:25:29,872 --> 00:25:33,831
<font color="gray">Major, I think we stand a good chance of</font>
<font color="gray">getting at least 90 percent of them.</font>
少校, 我觉得我们有很大可能可以消灭它们的９成

413
00:25:33,912 --> 00:25:36,221
<font color="gray">- How? We haven't got enough missiles.</font>
<font color="gray">- Oh, please, Major.</font>
- 怎么弄? 我们没有足够的导弹  - 哦, 拜托, 少校

414
00:25:36,312 --> 00:25:39,349
<font color="gray">Just knocking out half a dozen of them</font>
<font color="gray">will do very little good at all.</font>
只是干掉它们中的一两打的话, 完全没有多大收益

415
00:25:39,432 --> 00:25:40,660
<font color="gray">Let's try for them all.</font>
我们得尽力把它们全搞定

416
00:25:40,752 --> 00:25:43,869
<font color="gray">Look, miss, I know my business and</font>
<font color="gray">I'm telling you we haven't got enough missiles.</font>
听着, 小姐, 我知道我的情况, 我告诉你我们没有足够的导弹

417
00:25:43,952 --> 00:25:45,431
<font color="gray">Yes, you have.</font>
有, 你有

418
00:25:45,512 --> 00:25:47,980
<font color="gray">These things are coming in in a formation pattern.</font>
这些家伙是以一种编队阵型过来的

419
00:25:48,072 --> 00:25:52,304
<font color="gray">Now if you set your missiles carefully,</font>
<font color="gray">you can set up a chain reaction of explosions.</font>
现在如果你们仔细设定你们的导弹, 就可以引发链式爆炸

420
00:25:52,392 --> 00:25:55,031
<font color="gray">No, there isn't time to compute</font>
<font color="gray">all the relevant information.</font>
不行, 没有足够的时间来计算所有相关的因素了

421
00:25:55,112 --> 00:25:58,149
<font color="gray">- They'd be on top of us by then.</font>
<font color="gray">- Give me 30 seconds.</font>
- 到时候它们已经到我们头上了  - 给我３０秒

422
00:25:58,792 --> 00:26:01,022
<font color="gray">Give her what she asks, Major. 30 seconds.</font>
她要就给她吧, 少校, ３０ 秒

423
00:26:01,112 --> 00:26:04,627
<font color="gray">- But, sir, this is ridiculous!</font>
<font color="gray">- Just 30 seconds.</font>
- 但是, 长官, 这很荒谬!   - 就３０秒

424
00:26:06,272 --> 00:26:08,502
<font color="gray">- Hold for 30 seconds!</font>
<font color="gray">- Sir, that doesn't give us much time.</font>
- 暂缓３０秒!   - 长官, 给我们的时间不多了

425
00:26:08,592 --> 00:26:12,426
<font color="gray">All right, Sergeant, I know.</font>
<font color="gray">Countdown to begin at T minus 45 seconds.</font>
好了, 中士, 我知道. 开始４５秒倒计时

426
00:26:29,112 --> 00:26:31,068
<font color="gray">Here. Feed this into your computer.</font>
给, 把这个输入到你们电脑里面去

427
00:26:31,152 --> 00:26:34,030
<font color="gray">Do as she says. Now. I'll take over.</font>
按她说的做. 现在, 我来接管

428
00:26:34,112 --> 00:26:35,227
<font color="gray">Sir.</font>
长官

429
00:26:38,872 --> 00:26:41,067
<font color="gray">- You'd better be right.  - I am.</font>
- 你最好是对的  - 我当然是

430
00:26:43,592 --> 00:26:47,710
<font color="gray">T minus 45 seconds from...now.</font>
４５秒倒计时...开始

431
00:26:48,112 --> 00:26:49,511
<font color="gray">(WHIRRING)</font>

432
00:26:54,472 --> 00:26:58,704
<font color="gray">Once the Cybermen take over,</font>
<font color="gray">they'll destroy the Earth as we know it!</font>
一旦赛博人占领这里, 它们会毁灭地球的, 我们都知道!

433
00:26:58,792 --> 00:27:01,352
<font color="gray">You're just playing for time, aren't you?</font>
你只是在拖延时间, 对吗?

434
00:27:01,432 --> 00:27:04,868
<font color="gray">I'm trying to stop you</font>
<font color="gray">from destroying the human race!</font>
我是在尽力阻止你毁灭整个人类种族!

435
00:27:05,072 --> 00:27:06,824
<font color="gray">Your UNIT friends...</font>
你那些在 UNIT 的朋友...

436
00:27:07,392 --> 00:27:11,465
<font color="gray">You presumably managed to protect them</font>
<font color="gray">from the Cyber-control as well?</font>
估计你肯定设法保护了他们, 不让他们受到赛博控制波影响?

437
00:27:11,552 --> 00:27:13,144
<font color="gray">What are they planning?</font>
他们在谋划些什么?

438
00:27:13,232 --> 00:27:15,462
<font color="gray">I don't know what you're talking about.</font>
我不知道你在说些什么

439
00:27:18,032 --> 00:27:19,260
<font color="gray">Packer?</font>
Packer?

440
00:27:19,432 --> 00:27:20,547
<font color="gray"><i>Yes, sir.</i></font>
在, 先生

441
00:27:20,632 --> 00:27:23,942
<font color="gray">- Is the radio beam in the compound aligned yet?</font>
<font color="gray"><i>- Yes, sir, it's all ready.</i></font>
- 工业园的无线电波已经调校好了么?   - 是的, 先生, 都准备好了

442
00:27:24,032 --> 00:27:27,229
<font color="gray">Good. Then link the beam to the invasion fleet.</font>
好, 那把它跟入侵舰队的讯号连接起来

443
00:27:27,672 --> 00:27:29,264
<font color="gray"><i>Right, Mr Vaughn.</i></font>
好的, Vaughn 先生

444
00:27:31,192 --> 00:27:34,821
<font color="gray">Now whatever it is</font>
<font color="gray">your UNIT friends are trying to do...</font>
现在, 不管你在 UNIT 的朋友打算做什么...

445
00:27:34,912 --> 00:27:36,391
<font color="gray">it's too late.</font>
都来不及了

446
00:27:51,552 --> 00:27:56,706
<font color="gray">COMMUNICATOR: <i>The first transporter fleet</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>is being attacked and destroyed.</i></font>
第一支传送舰队已经被攻击了, 全部毁灭

447
00:27:56,792 --> 00:27:59,989
<font color="gray"><i>- You have betrayed us.</i>  - No!</font>
- 你背叛了我们  - 没有!

448
00:28:00,072 --> 00:28:04,384
<font color="gray"><i>The failure of this mission is due to you.</i></font>
这次任务的失败都是因为你

449
00:28:04,472 --> 00:28:07,942
<font color="gray"><i>We will now take over the invasion.</i></font>
我们现在要接管入侵行动

450
00:28:08,032 --> 00:28:10,421
<font color="gray">No! Wait! Give me time!</font>
不, 等等! 给我点时间!

451
00:28:10,512 --> 00:28:12,343
<font color="gray">I can stop this opposition!</font>
我可以组织那些抵抗者!

452
00:28:12,432 --> 00:28:14,900
<font color="gray"><i>There is no more time.</i></font>
不会有更多时间了

453
00:28:15,072 --> 00:28:17,267
<font color="gray"><i>We no longer need you.</i></font>
我们不再需要你了

454
00:28:17,552 --> 00:28:21,431
<font color="gray"><i>The Cyber-Megatron bomb will be delivered.</i></font>
即将发送赛博超级炸弹

455
00:28:21,512 --> 00:28:25,744
<font color="gray"><i>We must destroy life on Earth completely.</i></font>
我们必须完全摧毁地球上的生命

456
00:28:25,952 --> 00:28:28,307
<font color="gray"><i>Every living being.</i></font>
所有活着的生物

457
00:28:28,467 --> 00:28:30,635
<font color="gray">You can't do this! I won't let you!</font>
你不能这么做! 我不允许你这样!

458
00:28:30,727 --> 00:28:33,446
<font color="gray"><i>You cannot stop us.</i></font>
你阻止不了我们

459
00:28:33,527 --> 00:28:34,926
<font color="gray"><i>No one can.</i></font>
没谁能

460
00:28:35,327 --> 00:28:37,841
<font color="gray">Now you're beginning to understand</font>
<font color="gray">the Cybermen, Vaughn.</font>
现在你开始了解赛博人了, Vaughn

461
00:28:37,927 --> 00:28:39,485
<font color="gray">You can't make bargains with them!</font>
你不可能跟它们做交易!

462
00:28:39,567 --> 00:28:42,081
<font color="gray">I won't let them take over, I won't!</font>
我不允许他们接管, 我不!

463
00:28:44,847 --> 00:28:48,806
<font color="gray">You think you're indestructible?</font>
<font color="gray">Well, I can destroy all of you!</font>
你觉得你们是无法战胜的? 好, 我要摧毁你们全部!

464
00:28:49,127 --> 00:28:50,765
<font color="gray">(ELECTRONIC SIGNAL PULSATING)</font>

465
00:28:57,847 --> 00:29:00,077
<font color="gray">Packer! Packer! Where are you?</font>
Packer! Packer! 你在哪儿?

466
00:29:04,367 --> 00:29:09,525
<font color="gray">Vaughn, what have you done to us?</font>
<font color="gray">What have you done?</font>
Vaughn, 你对我们做了什么? 你做了什么?

467
00:29:15,507 --> 00:29:17,543
<font color="gray">(HUMMING)</font>

468
00:29:17,627 --> 00:29:19,060
<font color="gray">(SCREAMING)</font>

469
00:29:22,027 --> 00:29:23,824
<font color="gray">(ELECTRONIC SIGNAL PULSATING)</font>

470
00:29:29,167 --> 00:29:30,395
<font color="gray">Vaughn!</font>
Vaughn!

471
00:29:30,767 --> 00:29:33,361
<font color="gray">Where is the transmitter for the radio beam?</font>
无线电波发射器在哪里?

472
00:29:33,447 --> 00:29:35,642
<font color="gray">We can't fight them.</font>
<font color="gray">They're too powerful, too many of them.</font>
我们打不过它们的. 它们太强大了, 人数太多了

473
00:29:35,727 --> 00:29:38,082
<font color="gray">Oh, don't be a fool, man.</font>
<font color="gray">Where do we turn it off?</font>
噢, 别犯傻了, 伙计. 我们在哪里关掉它?

474
00:29:38,167 --> 00:29:42,126
<font color="gray">- At the compound, but they'll be there.</font>
<font color="gray">- Right. We must stop them.</font>
- 在工业园, 但它们快到那里了  - 好, 我们必须阻止它们

475
00:29:42,607 --> 00:29:45,963
<font color="gray">Brigadier, Brigadier, this is the Doctor.</font>
准将, 准将, 我是博士

476
00:29:46,047 --> 00:29:47,366
<font color="gray">Can you still hear me?</font>
你还能听到我吗?

477
00:29:47,767 --> 00:29:50,156
<font color="gray">Yes, Doctor, we heard everything.</font>
<font color="gray">What do we do?</font>
是的, 博士, 我们都听到了. 要我们做什么?

478
00:29:50,247 --> 00:29:51,760
<font color="gray"><i>There are only two possibilities.</i></font>
只有两种可能

479
00:29:51,847 --> 00:29:55,886
<font color="gray"><i>We must either cut off the transmitter</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>of the radio beam at the compound</i></font>
我们必须要么关掉工业园的无线电波发射器

480
00:29:55,967 --> 00:29:58,356
<font color="gray"><i>or destroy the Cyberman spaceship.</i></font>
要么摧毁赛博人的飞船

481
00:29:58,447 --> 00:29:59,800
<font color="gray">How much time do we have?</font>
我们有多少时间?

482
00:29:59,887 --> 00:30:02,526
<font color="gray"><i>Oh, I've no idea.</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>It could be minutes or hours.</i></font>
哦, 我 不知道. 有可能是几分钟或者几小时

483
00:30:02,607 --> 00:30:05,440
<font color="gray"><i>Depends how long it takes them</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>to prepare this bomb of theirs.</i></font>
取决于它们准备那个炸弹要多久

484
00:30:05,527 --> 00:30:08,246
<font color="gray">Well, destroying the spaceship</font>
<font color="gray">is going to take time.</font>
呃, 摧毁飞船需要不少时间

485
00:30:08,647 --> 00:30:10,603
<font color="gray"><i>Then there's only one chance.</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>The radio beam.</i></font>
那就只有一个机会了, 无线电波

486
00:30:10,687 --> 00:30:12,598
<font color="gray"><i>Er, wait. Vaughn.</i></font>
呃, 等等, Vaughn

487
00:30:13,367 --> 00:30:15,323
<font color="gray"><i>Now, Vaughn, will you help us?</i></font>
现在, Vaughn, 你会帮助我们吗?

488
00:30:15,407 --> 00:30:18,444
<font color="gray"><i>We must try to get to the controls</i></font>
<font color="gray"><i>of the radio beam.</i></font>
我们必须尽力赶到无线电波的控制台

489
00:30:18,527 --> 00:30:20,677
<font color="gray"><i>We'll never do it in time unless you help us!</i></font>
除非有你帮助我们, 否则我们不可能及时赶到!

490
00:30:20,767 --> 00:30:22,086
<font color="gray">You still think you have a chance?</font>
你还是觉得你有机会?

491
00:30:22,167 --> 00:30:26,046
<font color="gray">- Yes, if you'll help us!</font>
<font color="gray">- Help you? Why should I?</font>
- 是的, 只要你肯帮我们!   - 帮你们? 我应该吗?

492
00:30:26,127 --> 00:30:28,595
<font color="gray">Well, to save us! To save yourself!</font>
对, 救我们! 救你自己!

493
00:30:29,007 --> 00:30:32,841
<font color="gray">And if I survive, what future have I got?</font>
<font color="gray">What will the world do with me?</font>
如果我活下来, 我有什么未来? 这个世界会把我怎么样?

494
00:30:32,927 --> 00:30:34,997
<font color="gray">Oh, for heaven's sake,</font>
<font color="gray">stop thinking about yourself!</font>
噢, 老天啊, 别再只为你自己考虑了!

495
00:30:35,087 --> 00:30:38,284
<font color="gray">Think of the millions of people on Earth</font>
<font color="gray">who are about to die!</font>
想想地球上亿万的人就要死了!

496
00:30:39,167 --> 00:30:41,397
<font color="gray">Appealing to my better nature.</font>
呼唤我人性中善的一面

497
00:30:41,887 --> 00:30:42,876
<font color="gray">No.</font>
不

498
00:30:43,367 --> 00:30:46,245
<font color="gray">If I help you, it'll be because I hate them.</font>
如果我帮你, 也只是因为我恨它们

499
00:30:46,767 --> 00:30:49,600
<font color="gray">The Cybermen, my ''allies''.</font>
赛博人, 我的＂同盟＂

500
00:30:51,127 --> 00:30:54,517
<font color="gray">You think I'm mad,</font>
<font color="gray">that all I want is power for its own sake.</font>
你觉得我疯了, 觉得我想要的就只是权力本身

501
00:30:54,607 --> 00:30:56,563
<font color="gray">No, I have to have power.</font>
不, 我必须得有权力

502
00:30:56,647 --> 00:31:01,562
<font color="gray">The world is weak, vulnerable,</font>
<font color="gray">a mess of uncoordinated and impossible ideals.</font>
这个世界很虚弱、脆弱, 满是不协调、不现实的理念, 一团乱麻

503
00:31:01,647 --> 00:31:05,083
<font color="gray">It needs a strong man, a single mind.</font>
它需要一个强人, 一个独立的头脑

504
00:31:05,167 --> 00:31:07,635
<font color="gray">- A leader!  - Vaughn, will you listen?</font>
- 一个领袖!   - Vaughn, 你肯听吗?

505
00:31:09,807 --> 00:31:11,081
<font color="gray">Right.</font>
好

506
00:31:11,167 --> 00:31:14,055
<font color="gray">I'll help you to destroy them because I hate them.</font>
我会帮你摧毁它们, 因为我恨它们

507
00:31:14,347 --> 00:31:19,442
<font color="gray">They... destroyed my dream.</font>
它们...摧毁了我的梦

508
00:31:27,567 --> 00:31:29,159
<font color="gray">What are you doing?</font>
你在做什么?

509
00:31:29,247 --> 00:31:30,839
<font color="gray">We must destroy them!</font>
我们必须摧毁它们!

510
00:31:30,927 --> 00:31:33,487
<font color="gray">We want to get to</font>
<font color="gray">the radio transmitter control room!</font>
我们想要赶到无线电发射器的控制室!

511
00:31:33,567 --> 00:31:37,276
<font color="gray">The Cybermen don't know we're here yet.</font>
<font color="gray">Let's keep that element of surprise.</font>
赛博人还不知道我们在这里. 我们先保留这份惊喜吧

512
00:31:41,167 --> 00:31:43,362
<font color="gray">Come on, we'll try down here.</font>
快来, 我们试试这下面

513
00:31:55,727 --> 00:31:57,718
<font color="gray">(ELECTRONIC SIGNAL PULSATING)</font>

514
00:32:07,247 --> 00:32:09,602
<font color="gray">- Now they know we're here.  - Right.</font>
- 现在它们知道我们在这里了  - 对

515
00:32:10,047 --> 00:32:12,481
<font color="gray">Up there. We'll go over the roofs.</font>
上那边. 我们从屋顶过去

516
00:32:25,967 --> 00:32:27,286
<font color="gray">VAUGHN: That's it.</font>
就这样

517
00:32:28,327 --> 00:32:31,724
<font color="gray">(PANTING) That's where we've got to get to.</font>
<font color="gray">Down there.</font>
那是我们要去的地方, 那下面

518
00:32:38,487 --> 00:32:39,761
<font color="gray">Look out!</font>
小心!

519
00:32:41,887 --> 00:32:43,798
<font color="gray">(ELECTRONIC SIGNAL PULSATING)</font>

520
00:32:47,847 --> 00:32:49,280
<font color="gray">(CLATTERING)</font>

521
00:32:52,007 --> 00:32:53,281
<font color="gray">Look out!</font>
小心!

522
00:32:53,647 --> 00:32:54,841
<font color="gray">Come on!</font>
快点!

523
00:32:59,967 --> 00:33:01,286
<font color="gray">- Is this the only way down?  - Yes.</font>
- 只有这一条路下去吗?   - 是的

524
00:33:01,367 --> 00:33:02,800
<font color="gray">Come on, then.</font>
来吧, 那

525
00:33:09,527 --> 00:33:11,358
<font color="gray">Cybermen! Take cover!</font>
赛博人! 隐蔽!

526
00:33:14,767 --> 00:33:17,804
<font color="gray">They've got a main control switch</font>
<font color="gray">for the radio beam.</font>
无线电波有一个总开关

527
00:33:21,687 --> 00:33:25,402
<font color="gray">There doesn't seem to be</font>
<font color="gray">any Cybermen about at all. That's odd.</font>
这周围似乎完全没有赛博人, 这很奇怪

528
00:33:25,487 --> 00:33:27,942
<font color="gray">Well, let's not waste time, then.</font>
好, 我们别浪费时间了, 走

529
00:33:34,967 --> 00:33:36,559
<font color="gray">Look behind you!</font>
看你后面!

530
00:33:39,167 --> 00:33:40,839
<font color="gray">(ELECTRONIC SIGNAL PULSATING)</font>

531
00:33:46,287 --> 00:33:47,515
<font color="gray">(SCREAMING)</font>

532
00:33:51,527 --> 00:33:52,642
<font color="gray">Whoa!</font>
哇!

533
00:33:53,047 --> 00:33:54,844
<font color="gray">(SHOUTING)</font>

534
00:33:57,727 --> 00:34:00,287
<font color="gray">Doctor, get down! Right, bazooka!</font>
博士, 蹲下! 好, 火箭炮!

535
00:34:09,287 --> 00:34:10,686
<font color="gray">- You all right, Doctor?  - What?</font>
- 你没事吧, 博士?   - 什么?

536
00:34:10,767 --> 00:34:13,281
<font color="gray">Yes, yes, it's there, in that building.</font>
是的, 没事, 在那儿, 那栋建筑里

537
00:34:13,367 --> 00:34:16,120
<font color="gray">The radio transmitter control,</font>
<font color="gray">you've got to destroy it!</font>
无线电发射器, 你得毁掉它!

538
00:34:16,207 --> 00:34:18,118
<font color="gray">Leave it to us. Forward!</font>
交给我们吧. 前进!

539
00:34:18,207 --> 00:34:19,686
<font color="gray">Just a second.</font>
等一下

540
00:34:20,207 --> 00:34:21,640
<font color="gray">Oh, but I...</font>
噢, 但是我...

541
00:34:23,247 --> 00:34:25,681
<font color="gray">That's it, that's better. Sit still.</font>
就这样, 这样好多了. 坐着别动

542
00:34:28,287 --> 00:34:29,276
<font color="gray">(GUN FIRING)</font>

543
00:34:29,367 --> 00:34:31,323
<font color="gray">(SHOUTING)</font>

544
00:34:37,127 --> 00:34:38,401
<font color="gray">BRIGADIER: Grenades!</font>
手雷!

545
00:34:54,767 --> 00:34:55,995
<font color="gray">Bazooka!</font>
火箭炮!

546
00:35:21,687 --> 00:35:23,757
<font color="gray">That was just a dozen of them.</font>
这才只有十几个

547
00:35:23,847 --> 00:35:26,503
<font color="gray">I'd hate to have to meet a hundred.</font>
<font color="gray">Forward!</font>
我很讨厌得对付一百个. 前进!

548
00:35:26,587 --> 00:35:28,115
<font color="gray">Forward!</font>
前进!

549
00:36:19,607 --> 00:36:21,598
<font color="gray">There we are, all done and ready to go.</font>
我们到了. 全都搞定, 可以走了

550
00:36:21,687 --> 00:36:22,961
<font color="gray">(LAUGHING) Bye-bye.</font>
拜拜

551
00:36:23,047 --> 00:36:24,162
<font color="gray">- Bye-bye! - Bye.</font>
- 拜拜!   - 拜

552
00:36:24,247 --> 00:36:25,680
<font color="gray">A police box?</font>
一个警亭?

553
00:36:26,607 --> 00:36:28,325
<font color="gray">I don't believe it!</font>
我简直不敢相信!

554
00:36:36,287 --> 00:36:38,686
<font color="gray">(WHOOSHING)</font>

